                    </div>
                    <p>
                        Get up to 55% (€25) discount for a 1-way airport transfer service and get to your hotel/airport comfortably with Istanbul Tourist Pass®. <p>
                        <a href="{{path('price')}}">Buy a Pass</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
